#: server/activities/adjacent_numbers/AdjacentNumbersEditor.qml:100
msgctxt "AdjacentNumbersEditor|"
msgid "\"Start numbers\" must contain only numbers, and not be empty."
msgstr ""
"Οι \"Αριθμοί έναρξης\" πρέπει να περιέχουν μόνο αριθμούς και να μην είναι "
"κενό."

#: server/activities/adjacent_numbers/AdjacentNumbersEditor.qml:102
